name: Bounce Back
description: The retro boomerang roguelite adventure is now available as a limited edition NFT. Control with a mouse and keyboard or gamepad. Keep your coins and level when you die. There are 10 procedurally generated levels and a final boss. Win to unlock speed run mode. Originally released as a 13k zip with source on GitHub! How fast can you Bounce Back? https://github.com/KilledByAPixel/BounceBack ~ https://frankforce.com ~ https://twitter.com/KilledByAPixel
